fields.name: Lift Off® Energy Drink Lemon-Lime 10 tablets
fields.description:
Re-energise and hydrate your body with LiftOff Lemon-Lime flavour – a low-calorie, effervescent energy drink that contains caffeine powder and natural caffeine* from Guarana. At just 10kcal per serving and high in Vitamin C, LiftOff is a great, healthier alternative to fizzy sugary drinks.

Every serving provides 75 mg of caffeine, to help increase alertness and improve concentration.

fields.name: Herbalife24® Prolong Protein Drink Citrus 900g
fields.description:
Herbalife24® is the market’s first 24-hour sports nutrition line that is used by more than 190 sporting teams, athletes and events around the world to help them perform at their best.

Developed by experts in sports nutrition, Herbalife24® Prolong is a unique carbohydrate-protein drink enriched with vitamins and minerals, making it perfect to take during intensive or extensive exercise. It contains 6.8g whey protein to support the growth and maintenance of lean muscle mass.

fields.name: N-R-G Nature's Raw Guarana Caffeine Supplement 60 tablets
fields.description: N-R-G Nature’s Raw Guarana is a food supplement made from guarana, an ancient Amazonian seed that contains caffeine* to help support alertness and orange pekoe, a traditional black tea with a fine and rich flavour.

fields.name: Herbalife24® Hydrate Electrolyte Drink Orange 20 stick pack
fields.description:
Herbalife24® Hydrate is a calorie free electrolyte drink designed to encourage fluid consumption which contains 100% RDA of vitamin C to help reduce tiredness and fatigue. It provides B vitamins (B1, B2, pantothenic acid and B12) and calcium and magnesium, all contributing to normal energy-yielding metabolism.

Herbalife24® Hydrate is perfect for anyone who needs low-calorie hydration during intense training or after exercising.

fields.name: Herbalife24® CR7 Drive Sports Drink Acai Berry 540g canister
fields.description:
Being an athlete is a lifestyle that requires dynamic nutrition for your daily needs. Whether you’re playing an intense game of football or hitting the treadmill, you need products that will help you prepare, train and recover.  

Herbalife24® CR7 Drive is a delicious and refreshing carbohydrate-electrolyte drink for maintaining endurance performance during prolonged exercise, perfect for taking during exercise or sports.

It is an acai berry flavoured sports drink developed by experts in nutrition and international football star Cristiano Ronaldo that is proven to enhance the absorption of water during exercise* and help maintain endurance performance.**

fields.name: Herbalife24® Formula 1 Sport Protein Shake Vanilla Cream 524g
fields.description:
Inspired by our pioneering Formula 1 range, our Formula 1 Sport has been specially designed for the specific nutritional needs of athletes.

Formula 1 Sport contains 219 calories per serving to help manage your calorific intake and offers convenience, great taste and nutrition in one shake. It contains a unique blend of carbohydrates, high-quality protein, fibre, essential vitamins and minerals, making it a reliable, healthy meal to have before an intense workout.

fields.name: Formula 1 Protein Shake Banana Cream 550g
fields.description:
Meet Formula 1 Banana Cream: a quick-to-prepare nutritionally complete meal that delivers the perfect balance of protein, carbs, essential fats, fibre, vitamins and minerals. And it tastes great. 

Our Formula 1 shake is made from vegan ingredients and each serving contains 18g of protein, which supports the maintenance and growth of muscle mass. 

Packed with vitamins and minerals, fibre and essential micronutrients, our pioneering product comes in a range of exciting flavours.

Formula 1 is easy to prepare and has a deliciously creamy taste. It is a shake designed to meet your nutritional needs.

Enjoy every day as a healthy meal option.
